THE CHILDREN(2008)



Five families with many children gather during the Christmas holidays in a small cabin in the woods. So many children huddled in such a small space beds of course for an explosive cocktail, and when a child falls ill, things start to really take off. What appears to be a series of bizarre accidents end up a parent's life may be a very bloody end.

But it was an accident, or is there something terribly wrong with the kids?
